Modification notice (GPLv3 §5(a))
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Forked on:  2026-05-14
Fork base:  SteveTheKiller/KillerPDF
Fork by:    The Doodle Project, LLC

Summary of changes in this fork relative to upstream:

  1. Renamed product, package, namespace, and assembly from "KillerPDF" to
     "TDPdf". Versioning was reset to 1.0.0 under the new identity.
  2. All install-time identifiers updated to the new name:
        - executable:               TDPdf.exe
        - install directory:        %LOCALAPPDATA%\Programs\TDPdf\
        - ProgID:                   TDPdf.pdf
        - registry root:            HKCU\Software\TDPdf
        - Add/Remove Programs key:  HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\
                                    CurrentVersion\Uninstall\TDPdf
        - uninstall batch filename: tdpdf_uninstall.bat
  3. Publisher metadata in the Add/Remove Programs entry was changed from
     the upstream author to "The Doodle Project".
  4. The upstream author's personal branding ("Steve the Killer", and the
     thekiller.net and killertools.net domains) was removed from the UI,
     landing page, footer, README, and installer dialogs, as required by
     GPLv3 §7(e) when releasing a modified version. Upstream copyright
     and licensing notices in the source remain intact.
  5. Application icon replaced with a placeholder TD glyph at
     Resources/tdpdf-icon.ico.
  6. Landing-page assets specific to the upstream author (Umami analytics
     script, oosmetrics badges, og-image, screenshots) were removed.
  7. Documentation (README.md, CHANGELOG.md, copilot-instructions.md,
     release notes, and release.ps1) updated to reflect the new name,
     while preserving upstream attribution.

No code behavior was deliberately changed in the 1.0.0 rename commit;
all functional changes were inherited from the prior doodlemania2 fork
engineering and are documented in .github/release-notes/v1.0.0.md.

